&lt;li&gt;High EQ and empathy with a strong desire to build relationships with patients and willingness to help others&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attention to detail and strong organizational skills with unquestionable integrity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technological literacy to use various digital and virtual care platforms&lt;/li&gt;
